des:
"techWorld" is basically a trivia game based on computer and topics related to computers. Anyone with little knowledge of computers and information technology can play this game and can even score well. Total five questions will be asked and for each correct answer, one point is awarded to the user. This game will definitely enhance the knowledge of the users in computer science field.
 Enjoy it while playing and have a FUN....
